Finally, we add a column called track which will hold the categorical information for colouring dates by activity.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
dfr$track <- "Available"
dfr$track[dfr$day=="Sat"|dfr$day=="Sun"] <- "Weekend"
head(dfr)
```

