<div class="kable-table">

|date       |day |week |month |ddate |track     |
|:----------|:---|:----|:-----|:-----|:---------|
|2023-06-01 |Thu |22   |June  |01    |Available |
|2023-06-02 |Fri |22   |June  |02    |Available |
